- [Daniela] I'll be two minutes.

295
00:26:18,538 --> 00:26:21,583
GG and Marcus. Barbara and Mike.

296
00:26:25,003 --> 00:26:26,296
- Cheers.
- [Jason] Mmm.

297
00:26:26,796 --> 00:26:27,797
