wouldn't you?

312
00:27:00,288 --> 00:27:01,789
Oh, shit. I'd live there.

313
00:27:01,790 --> 00:27:03,457
- [Marcus, GG laughing]
- There you go.

314
00:27:03,458 --> 00:27:04,583
