- Just accept it.

325
00:27:31,278 --> 00:27:32,904
- Okay.
- Absorb it. Hey, buddy.

326
00:27:34,906 --> 00:27:35,991
- Hey.
- Hi.

327
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:39,202
