338
00:28:15,989 --> 00:28:17,281
- I'm so glad you could come.
- Hmm.

339
00:28:17,282 --> 00:28:19,074
- It's really nice to see you.
- So good to see you.

340
00:28:19,075 --> 00:28:21,327
Sorry, I was just in the middle
