469
00:37:04,643 --> 00:37:06,727
[Ryan whispering]
I'm so sorry. I didn't know.

470
00:37:06,728 --> 00:37:08,939
I don't know.
I don't know what's happening.

471
00:37:09,648 --> 00:37:12,149
[Ryan breathing shakily]

472
00:37:12,150 --> 00:37:13,610
